title: Gov. Whitmer, Rep. Ken Buck, DC Statehood
itunes:title: Gov. Whitmer, Rep. Ken Buck, DC Statehood
description:
Guests: Congresswoman for the District of Columbia, Eleanor Holmes Norton, Rick Davis, Partner at Stone Court Capital and former campaign manager for John McCain's 2008 presidential campaign, Michigan Governor Gretchen Whitmer, and Rep. Ken Buck, a Republican representing Colorado's 4th district..
